post.description:
### Description 
Deletes a specific Job. You must specify the `job_id` of the Job to delete.

### Description 
Gets a specific Job. Prints detailed information about the Job, including its state.

### Description 
Gets a list of all Jobs. You can use a query to get a filtered list of Jobs.

| Key | Description | Type | Required| |-------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|-----------|-------| |query||Query|| |role_binding_id||string|| |role_type|DOMAIN_ADMIN, WORKSPACE_OWNER, WORKSPACE_MEMBER |string|| |workspace_id||string|| |role_id||string|| |user_id||string||

post.description:
### Description 
You can create user. after create user you have to binding role to user.
See role-binding create api.
External type user do not need password.

### Description 
Update user info by given user_id

### Description 
Disable MFA for user. If this api is called, send email to user.

### Description 
Sets the user's refresh token timeout. This API can only be used by users with the `DOMAIN_ADMIN` role.
Min value is `1800` seconds and max value is `2592000` seconds

post.description:
### Description 
Google OAuth2, Keycloak OIDC, SAML are supported as external authentication.

### Description 
Create a workspace user. If the user does not exist in your domain, the user will be created in your domain and create a workspace user with the role.
If you want to create a workspace user with the existing user, you can use role-binding create api.

requestBody.description: | Key | Description | Type | Required| |-------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|-----------|-------| |user_id||string|True| |auth_type|LOCAL, EXTERNAL|AuthType|True| |reset_password|If reset_password is true, send email|boolean|True| |role_id|You can use custom role or managed role something like `managed-workspace-member`, `managed-workspace-owner` ,...|string|True| |password|When auth_type is LOCAL, password is required. |string|| |name||string|| |email||string|| |language|en,ko |string|| |timezone|UTC, Asia/Seoul |string|| |tags||Struct||

| Key | Description | Type | Required| |-------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|-----------|-------| |user_id||string|True| |workspace_id|For DOMAIN ADMIN this field is optional, but for WORKSPACE OWNER and WORKSPACE MEMBER this field is required. |string||
